{"tid":2225277,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"教宗可以落地獄了 - 馮睎乾","createTime":"2020-10-01T07:47:41.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-01T09:34:57.000Z","uid":25558,"like":46,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"1196dca484f300028e7e25313a3e3395071629d8","tid":2225277,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-01T07:47:41.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/columnist/20201001/ZBZHCS5XBNFAJLP7MHPDBOOLTE/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fcolumnist%2F20201001%2FZBZHCS5XBNFAJLP7MHPDBOOLTE%2F&d=2MheXYw%2FBwPqfvV%2BE34w15mLjsYRFZgpJr%2B2v3iO%2BBA%3D&h=c4bb94f4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fcolumnist%2F20201001%2FZBZHCS5XBNFAJLP7MHPDBOOLTE%2F&h=c3b39e08\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/columnist/20201001/ZBZHCS5XBNFAJLP7MHPDBOOLTE/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n教宗可以落地獄了 - 馮睎乾<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/nF8T8AaU62u_mU8iiz_5_HnZBVw=/840x625/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/NGHITKY47JAIBNBWHHTICQXFLU.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FnF8T8AaU62u_mU8iiz_5_HnZBVw%3D%2F840x625%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FNGHITKY47JAIBNBWHHTICQXFLU.png&h=b7d49c29&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n陳日君fb圖片<br />\n<br />\n真心愛教會的陳日君樞機，為了香港主教繼任人問題，冒着肺炎大疫風險，風塵僕僕飛到梵蒂岡，將一封信交給教宗方濟各的秘書，希望能跟教宗見面。結果陳樞機在旅館等待三日三夜，依然沒得到方濟各的回覆，只好落寞地離開羅馬。<br />\n<br />\n教宗這種傲慢涼薄的態度，連意媒也看不過眼。九月廿七日，羅馬《訊使報》（Il Messaggero）以「教宗給陳老樞機一記耳光：來羅馬求見，不予接待」（Schiaffo del Papa all&rsquo;anziano cardinale Zen: a Roma per incontrarlo, non lo ha ricevuto）為題報道，稱陳樞機雖然八十八歲，但「非常清醒和堅定」（lucidissimo e determinato）；又說他當初沒料到會受到「如此羞辱」（un trattamento tanto umiliante）。<br />\n<br />\n這篇報道還翻教宗的舊賬，.........................<br />\n<br />\n上星期我寫過，在不顯眼的細節上，往往最能顯示一個人的本性。日前意大利著名記者Marco Tosatti報道陳樞機不獲接見，也寫道：「如果一個人的善性也能在細節中見到，我不知道怎樣判斷某人&mdash;&mdash;一位領導者&mdash;&mdash;他在四天內找不到半小時接見一位年老神職人員。」<br />\n<br />\n陳日君很坦率地表示，任命親中的蔡惠民為主教，將帶來幾十年災難，又指教廷欲與中國續簽協議，想法瘋狂，如「附和魔鬼」。陳樞機的指控非常大膽。但觀乎方濟各的言行，尤其是細微處，我有理由相信教宗早已跟隨了魔鬼。今天香港的教友必須緊記：教會史上有不少道德敗壞的教宗，非但不能指引教徒升天堂，自己死後更要落地獄，例如但丁在《神曲》中寫過的尼古拉三世，以及他暗示的博義八世。<br />\n<br />\n據但丁所寫，地獄第三囊是留給犯下「買賣聖職罪」（simony）的神棍，包括樞機和教宗，詩中的尼古拉三世，正是任人唯親、貪慕富貴的教宗。他們死後，陰魂將倒插於一個小圓孔，腳掌不斷被火燒，類似中世紀的「倒頭栽」（propagginazione）死刑。為了討好極權國家而任命主教，是對聖職的莫大污辱，這樣的教宗絕對應該落地獄。"},{"pid":"fd9569f5dec9e8963c36e042c9dfc0a3add13775","tid":2225277,"uid":1524,"like":17,"dislike":1,"score":16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-01T07:56:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c633adb1443abc494f56552705c4ccd2072ce89","tid":2225277,"uid":146535,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-01T07:57:27.000Z","msg":"教宗真係唔一定代表正義"},{"pid":"c4811d444b6c97ba1af0c074f6e1ef54821d5f7c","tid":2225277,"uid":186388,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-01T08:40:48.000Z","msg":"滅教宗！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5cb060a05c66b90f2e82ba807572c0237ffcc3e9","tid":2225277,"uid":59898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-01T08:42:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/smile.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"829868b8029e468fc0675e1b857cc9641d74eb1d","tid":2225277,"uid":306340,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-01T08:43:54.000Z","msg":"預言書上最後一個教宗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"457d5c3414521ee06233f85c98861c9bc2a862d0","tid":2225277,"uid":2429,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-01T08:44:07.000Z","msg":"信伊斯蘭教了。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0929bac3a31433f466609c849f7b21d33317066a","tid":2225277,"uid":26168,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-01T08:46:22.000Z","msg":"見佢fing 撚開信眾d